WEBVTT

00:00.878 --> 00:03.139
Mystic Falls...
I was born here.

00:03.259 --> 00:04.508
This is my home.

00:04.510 --> 00:07.645
- And mine.
- And mine.

00:07.964 --> 00:10.831
For centuries,
supernatural creatures
have lived among us.

00:10.833 --> 00:13.834
They were
vampires, werewolves,
doppelgangers...

00:13.836 --> 00:15.736
- Witches.
- And even hybrids.

00:15.738 --> 00:18.089
And then
there's Elena.
She's one of us now.

00:18.091 --> 00:19.807
Why am I acting
like this?

00:19.809 --> 00:22.677
There may be one chance
to save her...
Nice ink.

00:22.679 --> 00:24.729
Tell him what
the hunter told you
the tattoo leads to!

00:24.731 --> 00:26.247
He said
there was a cure.

00:26.249 --> 00:28.382
No one must know
about the cure,
do you understand?

00:28.384 --> 00:32.153
The hunter holds the key,
and he'll stop at nothing...

