00:53.742 --> 00:57.778
You have any idea
what I've been through?

00:57.780 --> 01:00.748
I spent the last
two days chained up
by an original vampire.

01:00.750 --> 01:02.600
So you met Klaus?

01:02.602 --> 01:04.101
I only know him
by reputation.

01:04.102 --> 01:06.020
Apparently he's
a real monster.

01:06.022 --> 01:07.888
He's a vampire-werewolf hybrid.

01:07.890 --> 01:10.107
Do you know how hard
it is to kill them?

01:10.109 --> 01:11.642
From what I gather,
you have to...

01:11.644 --> 01:15.479
Remove their head,
or their heart.

01:15.481 --> 01:17.898
That is, according to lore.
I'm just speculating.

01:17.900 --> 01:19.717
I had to figure out
how to do it on my own.

01:19.719 --> 01:23.504
I could have used some
of this occult Professor
knowledge of yours.

01:23.506 --> 01:25.239
But then again,
you've always been slow

01:25.241 --> 01:26.791
when it comes
to providing answers.

01:26.793 --> 01:28.442
We had a deal.

01:28.444 --> 01:29.961
I'll give you
answers about
your hunter's mark

01:29.963 --> 01:31.445
when it's grown
to completion.

01:31.447 --> 01:34.281
In other words, kill
as many vampires as possible.

01:34.283 --> 01:36.617
Come on, Connor,
why do you think I sent
you to Mystic Falls?

01:36.619 --> 01:40.638
There's no shortage
of vampires. That town's
practically infested.

01:40.640 --> 01:42.807
Listen, there's a witch

01:42.809 --> 01:44.659
mixed up
in all this.

01:44.661 --> 01:46.310
She's important
to what I have planned.

01:46.312 --> 01:48.980
I want her to be kept
out of harm's way.

01:48.982 --> 01:51.148
Anybody gets in my way--

01:51.150 --> 01:53.351
anybody--

01:53.353 --> 01:54.968
they're dead.

01:54.970 --> 01:57.605
Ok...

01:57.607 --> 02:01.492
Sure, I'll occupy
her myself.

02:01.494 --> 02:04.328
Just do what you do.

02:05.614 --> 02:08.164
And the less
I know about it,
the better.

02:11.175 --> 02:21.323
